{
  "stem": "21786.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then I had a very unpleasant duty-- that is, from all the corpses, we had to take our golden teeth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That means when the body's stiff, you had to use a crowbar to open.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "We had the special commando which pulled out the teeth, and collect it in a sack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And every morning, it was given to the SS man on duty-- probably, I mean, promptly stole it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But the-- that was-- and then came Mengele, and asked all kinds of questions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- I had to explain it to him, just in one single sentences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In my presence, he never beat or never hit or never do anything for that it was-- he was probably too high here, delegated his responsibility to the lower-- lower kinds of ranks-- the Germans, usually from the occupied territories somewhere along the Danube, or from former Yugoslavia, or from Romania, or from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "His German-- their German was extremely poor, but they succeeded.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a relatively tall, good-looking man, who had a stony face.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't smile, didn't laugh, didn't make a grimace, didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Also, when I have seen him-- and I have seen him on the ramp-- where he went for a few hours, probably, to entertain himself-- being present at the selection of the people who were coming, sending them either to camp that was about every 10th, every 20th body which was capable of some work, or to their destruction.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people asked me if I have really seen him, personally.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, I can confirm that he was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was away from him a maximum of 50 meters.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And as such, sometimes we were ordered to bring into the camp some supplies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we got the hay wagon with the 14 men.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
